什么？

23
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:16,400
Why?
为什么？

24
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:19,200
I mean, we've had our ups and downs and we have the occasional disagreement but we're
我是说，我们有过起起落落，偶尔也有分歧，但我们

